# Fire Truck 3D Model for Water Salute Plugin
# Simple low-poly fire truck model
# Scale: 1 unit = 1 meter
# Origin: Center bottom of truck
# Facing: -Z direction (X-Plane convention)

# Material library
mtllib firetruck.mtl

